## 🧠 Chosen Software
This project focuses on **Git**, a distributed version control system developed by Linus Torvalds. Git is widely used for tracking changes in source code and enabling collaboration among developers.

---

## 📂 Repository Contents

| File Name | Description |
|----------|------------|
| script1.sh | System Identity Report |
| script2.sh | FOSS Package Inspector |
| script3.sh | Disk and Permission Auditor |
| script4.sh | Log File Analyzer |
| script5.sh | Open Source Manifesto Generator |

---

## ⚙️ System Requirements

- Linux system (tested on Arch Linux ARM)
- Bash shell
- Basic utilities: `grep`, `awk`, `du`, `ls`, `tail`
- Package manager: `pacman`

